<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login - Universitas Tunas Bangsa Jaya</title>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/@phosphor-icons/web"></script>
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; }
        .bg-custom-gray { background-color: #F4F5F7; }
        
        /* Animasi halus untuk input */
        input, select {
            transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-custom-gray min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl overflow-hidden grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 max-w-4xl w-full border border-gray-100">
        
        <div class="hidden lg:flex flex-col justify-between p-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-700 to-indigo-600 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
            
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-16 -mt-16 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-white opacity-5"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -ml-16 -mb-16 w-40 h-40 rounded-full bg-white opacity-5"></div>

            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
                    <div class="bg-white/10 p-3 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20">
                        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-white">
                            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="18" rx="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
                            <path d="M6 8h12M6 12h12M7 16h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h1 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-wide">UTBJ</h1>
                        <p class="text-xs text-indigo-100 uppercase tracking-wider">Research System</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">Sistem Pengajuan<br>Proposal Penelitian</h2>
                <p class="text-indigo-100 text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-90">
                    Platform terintegrasi untuk pengelolaan penelitian akademik di Universitas Tunas Bangsa Jaya. Efisien, Transparan, dan Akuntabel.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-indigo-200 font-medium">
                    <i class="ph-fill ph-shield-check text-lg"></i>
                    <span>Secure Access • v1.0.0</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center">
            
            <div class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Selamat Datang Kembali</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Silakan masuk ke akun Anda untuk melanjutkan.</p>
            </div>

            <form action="/login" method="post" class="space-y-5">
                
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5 ml-1">Email atau NIDN</label>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none text-gray-400">
                            <i class="ph ph-user text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <input name="identifier" type="text" placeholder="contoh@utbj.ac.id" required
                            class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm rounded-lg focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 focus:bg-white placeholder-gray-400 block" />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5 ml-1">Kata Sandi</label>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none text-gray-400">
                            <i class="ph ph-lock-key text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <input name="password" type="password" placeholder="••••••••" required
                            class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-2.5 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm rounded-lg focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 focus:bg-white placeholder-gray-400 block" />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5 ml-1">Masuk Sebagai</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                             <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none text-gray-400">
                                <i class="ph ph-briefcase text-xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <select name="role" class="w-full pl-10 pr-8 py-2.5 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm rounded-lg focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 focus:bg-white appearance-none cursor-pointer">
                                <option value="dosen">Dosen</option>
                                <option value="reviewer">Reviewer</option>
                                <option value="admin">Admin</option>
                            </select>
                            <div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 pr-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none text-gray-500">
                                <i class="ph-bold ph-caret-down"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-end pb-3 sm:pb-0 sm:justify-end">
                         <div class="flex items-center">
                            <input id="remember" type="checkbox" name="remember" class="w-4 h-4 text-indigo-600 bg-gray-100 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:ring-2 cursor-pointer">
                            <label for="remember" class="ml-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 cursor-pointer select-none">Ingat saya</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="pt-2">
                    <button type="submit"
                        class="w-full text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-indigo-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-5 py-3 text-center shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/30 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-0.5">
                        Masuk ke Dashboard
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-4">
                    <a href="#" class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500 hover:underline">Lupa kata sandi?</a>
                    <a href="#" class="text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900">Bantuan</a>
                </div>

            </form>

            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 text-center">
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                    Belum memiliki akun? 
                    <a href="#" class="font-medium text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500 hover:underline">Daftar Dosen Baru</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="absolute bottom-4 text-center w-full text-xs text-gray-400">
        &copy; 2026 Universitas Tunas Bangsa Jaya. All rights reserved.
    </div>

</body>
</html>